title: Trade Deadline, more like Dudline
itunes:title: Trade Deadline, more like Dudline
description:
A room filled with some heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling and Gregg Rosenthal bring you all of the latest news around the NFL including all the trade DUDLINE action (3:57), Andy Dalton's benching (25:29) and the Chargers firing Ken Whisenhunt (36:59). Stick around for a MNF matchup recap where the Dolphins lost again (44:27) and a TNF preview between the 49ers and Cardinals (51:36)
